        </section>

        <article class="panel plot-card"><div class="plot-head"><h2>Component waveforms: E<sub>x</sub>(t) and E<sub>y</sub>(t)</h2><p>The phase shift between these sinusoids determines the polarization state.</p></div><canvas id="timeCanvas" class="wide"></canvas></article>
